{"id":2657,"date":"2018-11-23T01:52:43","date_gmt":"2018-11-23T01:52:43","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/?p=2657"},"modified":"2021-02-27T03:48:44","modified_gmt":"2021-02-27T03:48:44","slug":"phong-cach-noi-hien-dai-va-bien-tau-tren-gioi","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/phong-cach-noi-hien-dai-va-bien-tau-tren-gioi\/","title":{"rendered":"Phong c\u00e1ch N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t Hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i v\u00e0 bi\u1ebfn t\u1ea5u tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Phong c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng chi ti\u1ebft, nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh d\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e9t \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n. Trong phong c\u00e1ch thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, c\u00e1c ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac s\u01b0 ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu ch\u00fa tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1o ra c\u00f4ng n\u0103ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng. Mang \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i, ti\u1ec7n nghi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng n\u0103ng. V\u1eady h\u00e3y th\u1eed xem phong c\u00e1ch N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t Hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebfn t\u1ea5u v\u00e0 thay \u0111\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u00e0 gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c n\u1ec1n v\u0103n h\u00f3a, \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u00e1c nhau!<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<ol>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Phong c\u00e1ch n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i Minimalism<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-2669\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/1-1-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"900\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/1-1-1.png 900w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/1-1-1-150x150.png 150w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/1-1-1-300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/1-1-1-768x768.png 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/1-1-1-250x250.png 250w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Phong c\u00e1ch n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i Minimalism ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e9t \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3 d\u00f9ng n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t g\u1ecdn g\u00e0ng. M\u00e0u s\u1eafc s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong phong c\u00e1ch thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t n\u00e0y ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu l\u00e0 m\u00e0u trung t\u00ednh v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng kh\u1ed1i h\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc \u0111a d\u1ea1ng nh\u01b0 h\u00ecnh vu\u00f4ng, h\u00ecnh ch\u1eef nh\u1eadt, h\u00ecnh tr\u00f2n\u2026<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a Phong c\u00e1ch n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i Minimalism l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, m\u00e0u s\u1eafc c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eabm t\u1ed1i ho\u1eb7c t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng. Ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn trong phong c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y l\u00e0 c\u00e1c chi ti\u1ebft h\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc \u0111a d\u1ea1ng nh\u01b0 h\u00ecnh vu\u00f4ng, h\u00ecnh ch\u1eef nh\u1eadt, h\u00ecnh tr\u00f2n. B\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t tr\u01a1n l\u00e1ng, \u00edt chi ti\u1ebft.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Phong c\u00e1ch n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i HI-Tech<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-2661\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"900\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/2.png 900w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/2-150x150.png 150w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/2-300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/2-768x768.png 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/2-250x250.png 250w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">K\u00ednh, kim lo\u1ea1i, \u0111\u00e1 hay c\u00e1c v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u nh\u00e2n t\u1ea1o kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u tr\u1ecdng t\u00e2m th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t theo Phong c\u00e1ch n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i HI-Tech. B\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf b\u1eb1ng ph\u1eb3ng, \u00edt chi ti\u1ebft.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Phong c\u00e1ch n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i HI-Tech \u0111\u1ec3 khoa tr\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00ednh th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 c\u1ee7a v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c tr\u1ed9n l\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng gian v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 m\u1edbi. M\u00e0u s\u1eafc s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00f3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf \u2013 d\u00f9ng m\u00e0u nguy\u00ean th\u1ee7y v\u00e0 m\u00e0u b\u00ea t\u00f4ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Phong c\u00e1ch n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i Scandinavian<\/span><br \/>\n<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-2662\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"900\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/3.png 900w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/3-150x150.png 150w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/3-300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/3-768x768.png 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/3-250x250.png 250w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">S\u1ef1 sang tr\u1ecdng, chu\u1ea9n m\u1ef1c v\u00e0 tinh t\u1ebf l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Phong c\u00e1ch n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i Scandinavian mang l\u1ea1i cho b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 kh\u00f4ng gian n\u00e0o. M\u00e0u s\u1eafc th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9ng trong nh\u1eefng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf Scandinavian l\u00e0 Tr\u1eafng, N\u00e2u, Kem v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0u g\u1ea7n g\u0169i t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng hoa v\u0103n m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, r\u00f5 n\u00e9t.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Phong c\u00e1ch n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i Industry<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-2663\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/4.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"900\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/4.png 900w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/4-150x150.png 150w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/4-300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/4-768x768.png 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/4-250x250.png 250w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Phong c\u00e1ch n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i Industry th\u01b0\u1eddng di\u1ec5n \u0111\u1ea1t s\u1ef1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, tr\u1ea7n tr\u1ee5i, m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t c\u00e1 t\u00ednh. B\u1ea3n ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a lo\u1ea1i phong c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y l\u00e0 kho\u1ea3ng kh\u00f4ng gian r\u1ed9ng l\u1edbn t\u1eeb nh\u00e0 m\u00e1y c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p, v\u1eady n\u00ean khi \u0111em phong c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y v\u00e0o n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t nh\u00e0 \u1edf s\u1ebd mang \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng gian m\u1edf, t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c r\u1ed9ng l\u1edbn b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eef c\u1eeda s\u1ed5 tr\u1ea7n v\u00e0 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n h\u00f3a n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t trong ph\u00f2ng. Phong c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t cho nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00ec s\u1ef1 ph\u00f3ng kho\u00e1ng, tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng gian m\u1edf t\u1ed1i \u0111a. M\u00e0u s\u1eafc s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu l\u00e0 tr\u1eafng, \u0111en, x\u00e1m, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 m\u00e0u \u0111\u1ecf g\u1ea1ch. \u0110\u1ed3 d\u00f9ng trang tr\u00ed n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t c\u0169ng s\u1ebd mang t\u00f4ng m\u00e0u n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed3 n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng v\u1eadt d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e9t h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<ol start=\"5\">\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Phong c\u00e1ch n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i Urban<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-2658\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/5.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"900\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/5.png 900w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/5-150x150.png 150w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/5-300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/5-768x768.png 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/5-250x250.png 250w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 phong c\u00e1ch r\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0a chu\u1ed9ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng cho nh\u1eefng c\u0103n h\u1ed9 chung c\u01b0 hay qu\u00e1n coffee v\u00ec n\u00f3 nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u1edbi v\u1ebb ngo\u00e0i ph\u00f3ng kho\u00e1ng, s\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edd. C\u00e1c phong c\u00e1ch thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i kh\u00e1c th\u01b0\u1eddng d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb g\u00f2 b\u00f3 b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t quy t\u1eafc n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 nh\u01b0ng Phong c\u00e1ch n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i Urban th\u00ec g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb tr\u00f3i bu\u1ed9c. N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t theo phong c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u v\u00e0 c\u00e1c t\u00ednh n\u0103ng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf phi ch\u00ednh th\u1ed1ng, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed nh\u1eefng m\u00f3n \u0111\u1ed3 mang t\u00ednh truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng hay hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o kh\u00f4ng gian. Nh\u1eefng v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u nh\u01b0 th\u00e9p, k\u1ebdm, b\u00ea t\u00f4ng, kim lo\u1ea1i, g\u1ed7&#8230; \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng, t\u1ea1o n\u00ean c\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e9t kh\u00f4ng gian r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i \u1edf ngay nh\u1eefng v\u00f9ng nh\u01b0 t\u01b0\u1eddng, x\u00e0 nh\u00e0, c\u0103n b\u1ebfp, ban c\u00f4ng&#8230; V\u1eady n\u00ean, khi b\u1ea1n b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o c\u0103n h\u1ed9 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf theo phong c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c nh\u01b0 \u0111ang h\u00edt th\u1edf b\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eddi ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng trong kh\u00f4ng gian k\u00edn.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<ol start=\"6\">\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Phong c\u00e1ch n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i Anh Qu\u1ed1c<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-2664\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/6.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"900\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/6.png 900w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/6-150x150.png 150w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/6-300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/6-768x768.png 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/6-250x250.png 250w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Phong c\u00e1ch thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng mang l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i, kh\u00f4ng g\u00f2 b\u00f3 cho ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0. M\u00e0u s\u1eafc kh\u00f4ng gian c\u0103n h\u1ed9 th\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng m\u00e0u s\u01a1n mang t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed1i l\u1eadp \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt c\u00e1c m\u00f3n \u0111\u1ed3 nh\u1ecf c\u00f3 gam m\u00e0u trung t\u00ednh, nh\u01b0 v\u1eady s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3 m\u00e0u s\u1eafc h\u00e0i h\u00f2a h\u01a1n. \u0110\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a phong c\u00e1ch thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng r\u01b0\u1eddm r\u00e0 v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u k\u1ef3, thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 thanh l\u1ecbch v\u00e0 tinh t\u1ebf v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ee7, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0a th\u00edch so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c phong c\u00e1ch thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, phong c\u00e1ch thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf Phong c\u00e1ch n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i Anh Qu\u1ed1c mang nhi\u1ec1u \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 pha tr\u1ed9n gi\u1eefa phong c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i v\u00e0 phong c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed3ng qu\u00ea. V\u1eady n\u00ean ch\u00fang ta d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y b\u00f3ng d\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng m\u00f3n \u0111\u1ed3 n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t sang tr\u1ecdng. S\u1ef1 ph\u1ed1i tr\u1ed9n n\u00e0y t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t n\u00e9t \u0111\u1eb9p r\u1ea5t ri\u00eang cho phong c\u00e1ch thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf Anh Qu\u1ed1c sang ch\u1ea3nh v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 nh\u1eadn ra.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<ol start=\"7\">\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Phong c\u00e1ch n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i M\u1ef9<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-2665\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/7.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"900\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/7.png 900w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/7-150x150.png 150w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/7-300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/7-768x768.png 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/7-250x250.png 250w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i ki\u1ec3u M\u1ef9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 t\u1ea1o s\u1ef1 ph\u00f3ng kho\u00e1ng, c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c t\u1ef1 do, r\u1ea5t \u0111a d\u1ea1ng \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng, t\u1eeb ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p m\u00e0u s\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0i tr\u00ed n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t theo t\u1eebng c\u00e1 t\u00ednh ri\u00eang bi\u1ec7t. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o, trang tr\u00ed t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 b\u1eadn t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn di\u1ec7n t\u00edch c\u0103n h\u1ed9. H\u1ea7u h\u1ebft, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng phong c\u00e1ch thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a phong c\u00e1ch c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p hay kim kh\u00ed, mang \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 nam t\u00ednh, tr\u1ea7m \u1ed5n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Trong nh\u1eefng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t theo phong c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i M\u1ef9, d\u1ec5 th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u nh\u01b0 g\u1ea1ch hay g\u1ed7 th\u00f4 ch\u01b0a qua gia c\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng. D\u00f9 nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng d\u1ec5 g\u00e2y c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu nh\u01b0ng trong thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf phong c\u00e1ch M\u1ef9 l\u1ea1i mang d\u00e1ng v\u1ebb h\u00e0i h\u00f2a, nh\u1edd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng v\u1eadt d\u1ee5ng n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 th\u1ea3m, gh\u1ebf sofa hay m\u00e0u s\u01a1n s\u00e1ng \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u n\u00e0y b\u1edbt s\u1ef1 th\u00f4 r\u00e1p.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<ol start=\"8\">\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Phong c\u00e1ch n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-2666\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/8.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"900\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/8.png 900w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/8-150x150.png 150w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/8-300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/8-768x768.png 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/8-250x250.png 250w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">N\u1ec1n v\u0103n h\u00f3a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n r\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0a th\u00edch tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, v\u1eady n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u khi phong c\u00e1ch n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0a chu\u1ed9ng. \u0110\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u1ed5i tr\u1ed9i trong phong c\u00e1ch thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 t\u1ed1i gi\u1ea3n, ti\u1ec7n \u00edch v\u00e0 h\u00e0i h\u00f2a v\u1edbi thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Gam m\u00e0u trung t\u00ednh tr\u1eafng, xanh r\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0u ti\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng l\u00e0m n\u1ec1n n\u00ean thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf phong c\u00e1ch n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n mang n\u00e9t h\u00e0i h\u00f2a, nh\u00e3 nh\u1eb7n. C\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 nhi\u1ec1u phong c\u00e1ch thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c, n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t th\u00f4ng minh r\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00fa tr\u1ecdng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong c\u0103n h\u1ed9 phong c\u00e1ch Nh\u1eadt v\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng cao ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng cho gia ch\u1ee7.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<ol start=\"9\">\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Phong c\u00e1ch n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-2667\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/9.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"900\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/9.png 900w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/9-150x150.png 150w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/9-300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/9-768x768.png 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/9-250x250.png 250w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t ki\u1ec3u H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c mang \u0111\u1eadm n\u00e9t v\u0103n h\u00f3a \u00c1 \u0110\u00f4ng, tuy nhi\u00ean n\u00f3 c\u0169ng mang nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng ri\u00eang bi\u1ec7t, th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u00f5 nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n trong thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf: S\u1ef1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n, ti\u1ebft ch\u1ebf, v\u00e0 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng s\u00e2u s\u1eafc c\u00e1c gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Phong c\u00e1ch thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i ki\u1ec3u H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng gam m\u00e0u \u0111a d\u1ea1ng nh\u01b0ng m\u00e0u ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea1o v\u1eabn l\u00e0 c\u00e1c gam m\u00e0u s\u00e1ng trang nh\u00e3 nh\u01b0 tr\u1eafng, v\u00e0ng nh\u1ea1t\u2026, ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u phong ph\u00fa, mang t\u00ednh th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 cao. M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a phong c\u00e1ch n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng s\u1ebd tr\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t tho\u00e1ng do c\u00e1ch thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng. Ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng su\u1ed1t v\u1edbi ph\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ecdc ho\u1eb7c ph\u00f2ng \u0103n, ph\u00f2ng tr\u00e0. \u0110\u00f4i khi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u0103n c\u00e1ch b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t t\u1ea5m b\u00ecnh phong ho\u1eb7c th\u00f4ng nhau b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch t\u1ea1o s\u00e0n nh\u00e0 c\u1ea5p b\u1eadc.<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Phong c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng chi ti\u1ebft, nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh d\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e9t \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n. Trong phong c\u00e1ch thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, c\u00e1c ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac s\u01b0 ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu ch\u00fa tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1o ra c\u00f4ng n\u0103ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng. Mang \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i, ti\u1ec7n nghi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":2671,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[154],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-2657","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-chia-se-kien-thuc"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2657","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp